Danny Tamberelli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danny_Tamberelli 0 Daniel Paul Tamberelli (born February 8, 1982) is an American actor, comedian and musician. He is best known for his roles as Little Pete in The Adventures of Pete and Pete, Arnold Perlstein in The Magic School Bus, one of the cast members for Nickelodeon's All That from seasons four through six and Jimmy De Santa in Grand Theft Auto V.
